{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction\/tracksvelocity"]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether this transaction will track the velocity of any animatable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties that change."}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"tracksVelocity","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV14tracksVelocitySbvp","symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"VelocityTrackingAnimation.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Animation\/VelocityTrackingAnimation.swift#L49"},"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tracksVelocity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":[{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS"},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15"},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0"},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0"},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction\/tracksVelocity","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tracksVelocity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property can be enabled in an interactive context to track velocity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"during a user interaction so that when the interaction ends, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation can use the accumulated velocities to create animations that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preserve them. This tracking is mutually exclusive with an animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"being used during a view change, since if there is an animation, it is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"responsible for managing its own velocity."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gesture onChanged and updating callbacks automatically set this property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to true."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This example shows an interaction which applies changes, tracking"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"velocity until the final change, which applies an animation (which will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"start with the velocity that was tracked during the previous changes)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These changes could come from a server or from an interactive control"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like a slider."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func receiveChange(change: ChangeInfo) {","    var transaction = Transaction()","    if change.isFinal {","        transaction.animation = .spring","    } else {","        transaction.tracksVelocity = true","    }","    withTransaction(transaction) {","        state.applyChange(change)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction/tracksVelocity":{"title":"tracksVelocity","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"tracksVelocity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether this transaction will track the velocity of any animatable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties that change."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction\/tracksVelocity","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction\/tracksvelocity","type":"topic"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}],"title":"OpenSwiftUI"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Transaction","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The context of the current state-processing update."}],"type":"topic"}}}